extends layout

block content
  .about-page.container
    h1 About Us
    p Welcome to Sportify — your ultimate destination for premium sports gear and athletic apparel.

    section.mission
      h2 Our Mission
      p We’re here to empower athletes of all levels by providing top-quality equipment, apparel, and accessories — all in one place.

    section.values
      h2 What We Value
      ul
        li Quality products from trusted brands
        li Customer-first service
        li Promoting a healthy, active lifestyle
        li Sustainability and ethical sourcing

    section.story
      h2 Our Story
      p Sportify was founded in 2018 by a team of sports lovers who were frustrated by the lack of reliable online options. Since then, we’ve grown into a trusted platform serving thousands of athletes around the world.

    section.brands
      h2 Trusted Brands
      p We proudly stock leading brands like:
      ul
        li Nike
        li Adidas
        li Under Armour
        li Puma
        li Wilson

    section.contact
      h2 Get in Touch
      p Have questions or feedback? Reach out!
      ul
        li Email: support@sportify.com
        li Phone: (123) 456-7890
        li Follow us on social: 
          a(href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/sportify") LinkedIn
          | , 
          a(href="https://www.tiktok.com/@sportify") TikTok
          | , 
          a(href="https://instagram.com/sportify") Instagram
          | , 
          a(href="https://twitter.com/sportify") Twitter

  footer
      p &copy; #{new Date().getFullYear()} Sportify. All rights reserved.